  "description": "GKE Node Auto-Provisioning (NAP) \u00e2\u20ac\u201d the GA, Google-native Karpenter equivalent. Visualizes the elastic, Spot, scale-to-zero capacity that the ci-spot Custom ComputeClass provisions for bursty CI agents, alongside the static platform pool. Node membership (Spot / ci-spot) is read from the node TAINTS via kube-state-metrics (kube_node_info / kube_node_spec_taint), which scripts/03-observability.sh keeps even in the lean/free Grafana Cloud profile (a tiny node-inventory allow-list), so this board works in all observability modes.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Node Auto-Provisioning (NAP) \u00e2\u20ac\u201d elastic Spot CI nodes\nGKE **Node Auto-Provisioning** is the GA, Google-native equivalent of Karpenter. The `ci-spot` **Custom ComputeClass** ([`infrastructure/compute-classes/ci-spot.yaml`](../infrastructure/compute-classes/ci-spot.yaml)) makes NAP auto-create **Spot, scale-to-zero** node pools for bursty CI build agents (Spot-first c3/n2/c2/e2 \u00e2\u2020\u2019 on-demand fallback). The long-lived platform stays on the **static** `jenkins-2026-pool`. See [`docs/201`](../docs/201-ARCHITECTURE.md) and [`docs/501`](../docs/501-PLATFORM_OPERATIONS.md).\n\n**How to read it:** watch **Spot nodes** rise when a pipeline build starts and fall back toward **0** a few minutes after it finishes (consolidation) \u00e2\u20ac\u201d that is the scale-to-zero cost profile. The **Static pool** line should stay flat (the platform). *No data?* It reads node taints from kube-state-metrics (`kube_node_spec_taint`); `03-observability.sh` keeps that tiny node-inventory slice even in lean/free-tier mode, so check KSM is up (`kube-state-metrics` pod) and that a build has actually triggered a Spot node.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "count(kube_node_info)",
          "legendFormat": "nodes",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Total nodes",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "Nodes labelled cloud.google.com/gke-spot=true \u00e2\u20ac\u201d the ephemeral capacity NAP provisions for the ci-spot ComputeClass.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "fixedColor": "orange",
            "mode": "fixed"
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "count(kube_node_spec_taint{key=\"cloud.google.com/gke-spot\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "spot",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Spot CI nodes (NAP)",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "description": "Nodes auto-created for the ci-spot Custom ComputeClass (GKE auto-labels them cloud.google.com/compute-class=ci-spot).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "fixedColor": "purple",
            "mode": "fixed"
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "count(kube_node_spec_taint{key=\"cloud.google.com/compute-class\",value=\"ci-spot\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "ci-spot",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "ci-spot ComputeClass nodes",
